<div style="margin-top: 20px;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class='row'>
      <div class='span12'>
        <%= link_to (image_tag '/assets/domosaics_banner.png', :alt=>'DoMosaics'), 'http://www.domosaics.uni-muenster.de' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    <br />

<div class='row'>
  <% if @user.nil? %>
    <div class='alert alert-error' style='margin-top:10px; text-align:center;'>
      <b>Sorry</b> - unable to find download token. <a href="/#download">Sign-up again or have download token resent</a>
    </div>
  <% else %>
  <div class='span8'>
  <p style='text-align:justify;>'>
  Hi <b><%= @user.name %></b>, <br />
  before you proceed to download, please take note of the conditions stated below. If you should have any questions, comments or bug reports, please send a mail to
  <a href="mailto:domosaics@uni-muenster.de">domosaics@uni-muenster.de</a></p>
  Thanks, and enjoy.
  </div>
  <div class='span2 offset2'>
    <img src='/assets/download_arrow.png'>
  </div>
</div>
<b>Please Note</b>: 
<hr />
<ul>
<li>DoMosaics is still under development. Keep that in mind when you use DoMosaics for your research</li>
<br />
<li>We will contact you <b>exactly one more time</b> to notify you that the development phase is complete, and to invite you to download the released version</li>
<br />
<li>We do intend to release DoMosaics as open source, but until the final release please do not <b>copy/use any of the code</b> and <b>do not redistribute DoMosaics</b></li>
